parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting gears
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission makes a whining or grinding noise
the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission hesitates or slips when shifting gears
the vehicle jerks or lurches when accelerating
the transmission makes a whining or grinding noise
the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the key to be removed while the vehicle is in motion, leading to loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key can be removed from the ignition switch while the vehicle is in motion
the key is loose in the ignition switch
the key can be removed while the vehicle is in accessory or run settings
the vehicle stalls
the key releases from the ignition switch while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy improperly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, leading to increased risk of injury or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag system is faulty
the airbag may not deploy properly in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The rear wheel collapses or bends inward
the vehicle pulls to one side
the rear suspension makes a loud noise
or the vehicle vibrates excessively.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause the vehicle to crash, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes feel soft or spongy
the vehicle takes longer to stop
or the brakes make a grinding or screeching noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the control arm can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
